      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "title": "Questions To Answer",
        "summary": "- Which hosted auth and database layer will own these four records in deployment?\n- Should every user start with exactly one workspace, or do we need multi-workspace support immediately?\n- What installation and repo-mapping edits belong in onboarding versus later settings?",
