      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "body": "Goal: Implement the concrete hosted users schema\nStatus: todo\n\nTasks in scope:\n1. Create the persisted user records\n2. Attach GitHub through auth_identities\n3. Resolve the workspace bundle on sign-in\n4. Make work the default save destination\n\nOpen questions:\n1. Which hosted stack will own the first users slice?",
        "priority": "high",
